### 2. A Component Reference Comment Block

For any NEW component you ask Cursor to build, paste this at the top of your prompt as a "component passport." It takes 10 seconds and prevents drift:
```
COMPONENT PASSPORT:
- Act: [1 or 2]
- Background: [off-white grid / dark slate]
- Primary stat displayed: [e.g. "labor-years"]
- Emotional target: [e.g. "alarming" / "educational" / "revelatory"]
- Font tier needed: [Tier 1 money stat / Tier 2 era label / Tier 3 body]
- Interactive? [yes/no -- determines neumorphic shadows]
- Maximalist moment? [yes/no -- determines burst animation]